replies.body:
LOL you guys are all sooo off

1. PvP Team easily takes the cake as the best team on avicus with their all star line up, perfect scrim record, and amazing communication.

2. A close 2nd, Furium comes in at number 2 because they have the owner on their team and he could, quite possibly, rig the entire tournament to lead his team to victory!

3. ,ADAMCHENCLIQHAK is a no brainer to be near the top of this list! this team uses its intimidating name to weaken it's foes, and backs up that ferocious name with some amazing pvpers with awesome username choices, I think ADAMCHENCLIQHAK has an great chance in th next tournament.

4. CrookArmy comes in with a solid 4th place on the list due to the teams solid walls background! This team can not only get full diamond on every single walls map, but can also back that up with some mediocre pvp ability and sub par knowledge of nebula strategy. They have a good chance of making it to the finals if they work on their communication!

5. The 5th and final team on my list is going to have to be AvicusOG. Although undermanned and underrated compared to the other amazing teams on this list, AvicusOG is made up of only the top tier original gangsters of avicus and could easily shoot up all the other teams and scare them off with their incredible amount of street cred. Look out folks because AvicusOG could make a surprising performance in the next tournament!

Runner Up: Wizerds, although displaying some elementary spelling abilities, could quite possibly have the man and willpower to overcome these other highly skilled teams! Not to mention they claim to enjoy magic, which could be used to stun and dazzle opponents, leading wizerds to a sneaky victory!!
